OL,4,Ctomorrow
OL,6,
OL,7,F The programme moves to Salford,
OL,8,Fjoining BBC Breakfast.
OL,9,F The format will change, with the
OL,10,Fprogramme running for an hour in total
OL,11,F` including the 10-minute regional opt.
OL,12,F Some of the regular presenters are
OL,13,Fchanging.
OL,14,F Publicity suggests the programme
OL,15,Fwill be presented from the Breakfast
OL,16,Fsofa but with a virtual newsroom
OL,17,Fbackdrop.
OL,19,FThe move to Salford in itself should
OL,20,Fnot be a problem.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/8
