OL,6,FThe success of Breakfast and 5 Live
OL,7,Fdemonstrates that national news
OL,8,Fprogrammes need not be presented from
OL,9,FLondon.
OL,11,FWhat matters is where reporters are
OL,12,Fworking. They are not affected by the
OL,13,Fchange.
OL,15,FThe question of the format is a
OL,16,Fdifferent one though.
