OL,6,FThe question then is what should
OL,7,Fhappen during the last 15 minutes.
OL,9,FThe expectation is that we will see
OL,10,Fmore of the human and regional stories
OL,11,Fwhich work well on Breakfast. But if
OL,12,Fthe regional news opt provides some
OL,13,Fpunctuation to the programme, they
OL,14,Fwill be clearly separated from the
OL,15,Fmain news of the day.
OL,17,FIt could be hard to judge the content
OL,18,Fproperly over the next few weeks
OL,19,Fthough ` especially as the election
OL,20,Fcampaign intensifies.
