OL,6,FWill the extra time simply include the
OL,7,Fsort of stories which might have been
OL,8,Fsqueezed out?
OL,10,FSome may wonder about the wisdom of
OL,11,Fusing the Breakfast sofa for an actual
OL,12,Fnews bulletin.
OL,14,FLet's see how it looks. But, of
OL,15,Fcourse, many regional programmes have
OL,16,Fdone this for years.
OL,18,FThe extension to the One also has
OL,19,Fimplications for the rest of BBC One
OL,20,Fdaytime.
