OL,3,CSalford-based BBC News at One launches
OL,4,Ctomorrow
OL,6,FAlong with the recent extensions to
OL,7,FBreakfast and Morning Live, there's
OL,8,Fnow an extra hour of live daytime
OL,9,Foutput on BBC One each day ` or, to
OL,10,Fput it another way, an hour less of
OL,11,Fother material to commission.
OL,13,FDoctors has already ceased production
OL,14,Fand will finally come off air towards
OL,15,Fthe end of the year. (It will be
OL,16,Ftaking its normal summer break
OL,17,Fshortly.)
OL,19,FBBC One daytime is a success story `
OL,20,Fin no small measure because of
OL,21,FBreakfast and the News at One.
