OL,6,FThe tabloids have been full of stories
OL,7,Fclaiming the future of This Morning on
OL,8,FITV 1 is in doubt. Yet few have
OL,9,Fcelebrated the BBC's achievements ` a
OL,10,Ffar cry from the early 90s when the
OL,11,FBBC's daytime ratings were so
OL,12,Fdiabolical that some might have
OL,13,Fquestioned whether original mid-
OL,14,Fmorning TV was a waste of resources.
OL,16,FThe News at One wins three times the
OL,17,Faudience of the ITV Lunchtime News.
OL,19,FThis revamp must build on that
OL,20,Fsuccess. It is too important a
OL,21,Fprogramme to compromise.
